        Description copied from interface: IKandyAddressBookService
        Returns the domain contacts as IKandyContact objects in an array in the response callback. If operation failed, return an error. Filters contact according to filterType and text in textSearch.

        isCaseSensitive - Boolean value indicating whether or not the search is case sensitive.
        search_string - the text to search in the fields indicated by filterType
        listener - A callback with IKandyContact objects in an array if operation succeeded, or error if operation failed.
